This one also needs a delay.

00:10:03.405 --> 00:10:08.580
This is data aos delay and 1000 milliseconds,

00:10:08.580 --> 00:10:12.995
the duration we also going to increase this to be 150 too,

00:10:12.995 --> 00:10:17.390
and then grab this and we can add this for the last line too.

00:10:17.750 --> 00:10:20.555
Paste this in as an attribute.

00:10:20.555 --> 00:10:23.875
We can increase the delay to be 200 milliseconds,

00:10:23.875 --> 00:10:27.355
keeping the same duration and animation name.

00:10:27.355 --> 00:10:30.665
Go to the browser and reload,

00:10:30.665 --> 00:10:34.290
leaving us with some nice animation effects.

00:10:34.290 --> 00:10:38.755
There is one thing though to take care of before I wrap this video up.

00:10:38.755 --> 00:10:42.445
One of the things you will notice since adding in this animation,

00:10:42.445 --> 00:10:46.295
is we can now scroll to the right of the page when it first loads.

00:10:46.295 --> 00:10:49.870
This is because our animations, which slide in,

00:10:49.870 --> 00:10:54.375
will start off the edge of the page and then slide into our view.

00:10:54.375 --> 00:10:56.890
Since the content started off the page,

00:10:56.890 --> 00:11:01.285
the browser now things that the page is much wider than it's intended to be.

00:11:01.285 --> 00:11:03.560
All we need to do to fix this is to tell

00:11:03.560 --> 00:11:08.110
the browser to hide any content which overflows the page.

00:11:08.110 --> 00:11:10.800
We can do this by adding a overflow on

00:11:10.800 --> 00:11:16.500
the x-axis and we are going to do this in the body section of our style sheets.

00:11:17.240 --> 00:11:20.630
Let's scroll up to our global styles.

00:11:20.630 --> 00:11:25.340
We can declare how we want to handle any overflow on the x-axis,

00:11:25.340 --> 00:11:28.205
which is from the left to the right of the page.

00:11:28.205 --> 00:11:31.920
Change this to a value of hidden. Let's save this.

00:11:31.920 --> 00:11:36.860
Now if we go back to the browser and scroll back onto the main content section,

00:11:36.860 --> 00:11:43.230
hit reload and now this overflow property is stopping us from scrolling off the page.

00:11:43.340 --> 00:11:48.470
We'll also add more of these animations as we progress through the course.

00:11:48.470 --> 00:11:54.610
But feel free to swap out any of these animations with different ones to suit your style.

